Description
We are an IT firm providing outsourced technical support and IT solutions designed on a per client basis to the SMB market throughout the L.A, Ventura and Orange County areas. We are looking for an ambitious, Level II Technical Support Analyst that wants to grow with our company. We are a small and energetic group growing at a fast pace.
DESCRIPTION OF RESPONSIBILITIES AND DUTIES:
Provide network/technical administration and troubleshooting for all versions of Windows clients and servers;
Provide support for Active Directory, IIS, Terminal Services, DNS, DHCP, all Exchange versions and any Server related applications and/or services;
